{"tid":2430350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國2月製造業PMI跌新低 凸顯經濟復甦脆弱","createTime":"2021-03-03T01:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T07:36:40.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e706636c71539fd05c06a16f6acbef675d24d8ee","tid":2430350,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:19:17.000Z","msg":"由於海外需求疲軟和中共病毒（武漢肺炎）疫情爆發拖累產出，中國勞動力市場上個月持<br />\n續受到衝擊，其2月工廠活動擴張速度降至九個月新低。<br />\n <br />\n財新傳媒和研究公司Markit週一（3月1日）指出，中國製造業的採購經理人指數（PMI）<br />\n經2月季節性調整後跌至50.9，為九個月低位，是去年5月以來最低水平。遜於路透調查的<br />\n估值。<br />\n <br />\n儘管有分析師在中國（中共）聲稱成功杜絕確診病例後，預計該國全年增長將強勁反彈，<br />\n但週一發布的報告似乎駁回了這些預測，顯示製造業放緩凸顯了中國經濟持續復甦的脆弱<br />\n性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Pr2s69\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Pr2s69&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiulznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=1337097b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Pr2s69</a>"},{"pid":"a164cd6e715b6986ed115daf0131c8352526090d","tid":2430350,"uid":60924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:20:06.000Z","msg":"內循環呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c346a5a75c79519cd3887264631a00cb1f306e38","tid":2430350,"uid":299694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"數據假㗎，雜總話支國經濟好好，唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a161c3377415b6ef11472c2b1f20ddf1be75ab2f","tid":2430350,"uid":264121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:36:40.000Z","msg":"脫左貧啦，仲做？"}]}